PrecisAmendment to the PENITENTIARY SERVICES REGULATIONS providing that, except for private family visits with male inmates, female inmates are not to associate with male inmates, except under the constant supervision of an employee of the Correctional Service of Canada.

precis:
Amendment to the PENITENTIARY SERVICES REGULATIONS providing that, except
for private family visits with male inmates, female inmates are not to
associate with male inmates, except under the constant supervision of an
employee of the Correctional Service of Canada.
